</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_238" id="117v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_238_r1l16"><expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> Rüſwurm <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>elt<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_238_r1l17"><expan>Vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>fruntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> beuor / <expan>Lıeb<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> / Als du vns <expan>geſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> haſt / vvie </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_238_r1l19"> <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> Haller vnſer Ratgeſell / 
<del rend="strikethrough">dein </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_238_r1l18">von dir </ab></add> auf <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> Lantfrid geredt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſüll / . </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_238_r1l20">
<del rend="strikethrough">Nu ıſt </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_238_line_1576749844071_9107">dauon vviſſen vvir </ab><ab facs="#facs_238_line_1576749846877_9112">nicht So iſt auch </ab></add> <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> Haller yecʒund nicht anheim / Doch ſo vvöllen wir dir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_238_r1l23"><expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> ein geleitt <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> für vns vnd die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>vngeu<ex>er</ex>lich</expan></del> / Alſo wenn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_238_r1l24">du <expan>hiecʒwiſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> nehſten ſant <expan>Laurencʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> tag cʒü vns <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_238_r1l25">wilt / So ſolt du das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> cʒwen tag cʒü vns vnd <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_238_r1l27"><expan>vngeu<ex>er</ex>lıch</expan> / . <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>vts<ex>upra</ex></expan> . </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_238" id="117v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> Rüswurm <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>elt<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>fruntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> bevor. <expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan>, als du uns <expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        hast, wie <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> Haller, unser ratgesell, <add>von
                            dir</add> auf <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> lantfrid geredt
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> süll, <add>davon wissen wir nicht; so
                            ist auch</add>
<expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> Haller yeczund nicht anheim. Doch so wöllen
                        wir dir <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> ein geleitt
                            <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> für uns und die
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>. Also wenn du
                            <expan>hieczwisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<app><note><q type="date">nehsten sant <expan>Laurencze<ex>n</ex></expan> tag</q>10.08.1409</note></app> czü uns
                                <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> wilt, so solt du das
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> czwen tag czü uns und
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> uns,
                        <expan>ungev<ex>er</ex>lich</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>uts<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
